OL,3,CWhat are the Tories, Labour and Lib
OL,4,CDems promising infected blood victims?
OL,6,FITV News Health and Science Producer
OL,7,FPhilip Sime reports
OL,9,FOn May 20, a damning report into the
OL,10,Finfected blood scandal called for
OL,11,Fnational recognition of the disaster
OL,12,Fand compensation without delay.
OL,14,FIn the wake of the 2,527-page report,
OL,15,Fthe government promised compensation
OL,16,Fwould be paid to all those "infected
OL,17,For affected" by the end of the year.
