OL,3,CWhat are the Tories, Labour and Lib
OL,4,CDems promising infected blood victims?
OL,6,FThe report from the Infected Blood
OL,7,FInquiry found the scandal "could
OL,8,Flargely have been avoided", and that
OL,9,Fpeople were knowingly exposed to
OL,10,Fcontaminated blood products.
OL,12,FIt also found there was a "pervasive"
OL,13,Fcover-up to hide the truth from
OL,14,Fsuccessive governments, medics and NHS
OL,15,Fofficials.
OL,17,FBut with the general election looming,
OL,18,Fwhat do the Conservative, Labour and
OL,19,FLiberal Democracts manifestos promise
OL,20,Fto deliver to the victims?
